{"title":"黑心的市长","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3095","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>A市有一条长Nkm的高速公路。有M个人各自想承包下a~b的路段。</p>\n<p>这不给点钱是不行的，每人给ci元。</p>\n<p>市长很黑心，想赚很多钱。如果同时允许多人承包同一路段，是不行的。</p>\n<p>求市长最多赚多少钱。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>正整数N  M</p>\n<p>M行，ai，bi，ci。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>钱数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10 3</p>\n<p>1 5 10</p>\n<p>4 7 9</p>\n<p>7 10 8</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>18</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>M《=500，N《=10<sup>14</sup>，ci《=10<sup>9</sup>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}